    Sim is an event driven simulation that simulates a certain number of cashiers that service customers that come to the shop from 06:00 - 21:00.
    SimTest

    SimTester
    SimTester is the main class that gathers the data from the given input.txt and runs the simulation of the CoffeeShop with the provided data.
